snippet.title: Air Guitar Warrior Gamepad Edition - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
Air Guitar Warrior Gamepad Edition is a rhythm shooter for everyone who enjoys a good measure of over-the-top rock attitude in their indie games. Tap buttons in rhythm to shoot enemies with weaponized guitars. Ride epic mounts like motorbikes and cyber-dinosaurs across 50 hand-painted levels inspired by the history of rock. Features a unique interactive soundtrack with 19 tracks by musicians Mika Tyyskä / Mr. Fastfinger and Samppa Siurala.

Out now Xbox One - http://airguitarwarrior.com/gamepad
